requirements:
tested under 0.16.2

1.how to build this plugin?
a.maven combile
<pre>
mvn clean
mvn package
</pre>

b.drop the jar file to your elasticsearch plugin folder:

like: elasticsearch/plguin/es-partial-update/


2.how to play with this plguin?

a.first,let's do a index
<pre>
curl -XDELETE http://localhost:9200/index/type1/1/
curl -XPOST http://localhost:9200/index/type1/1/ -d'{"name":"medcl","blog":"http://log.medcl.net"}'
</pre>
b.now let's get it,check it
<pre>
curl -XGET http://localhost:9200/index/type1/1/
</pre>
c.now let's update it
<pre>
curl -XPOST http://localhost:9200/index/type1/1/_update -d'{"name":"medcl?","time":"2011-1-1"}'
</pre>
d.let's get the document again,check...
<pre>
curl -XGET http://localhost:9200/index/type1/1/
</pre>
